" We really thought that they were being funny, but no more than 5-10 seconds later, two dozen are handed to us....BIG RED FLAG...There is nothing more simple than a perfectly shucked oyster, plump, full with all is juice, and most importantly, free from the second muscle that holds the oyster in place.
These oysters were none of that with the sunken in "pre-shucked" look you would see in a buffet totally disguised by the green onions, ponzu, and hot sauce  Some were even stabbed in half by the oyster knife and still clung to the shell because of that muscle on the bottom.
